``Pyrat Bay``: Python Radiative Transfer in a Bayesian framework


Install as:

.. code-block:: shell

    pip install pyratbay

Or:

.. code-block:: shell

    conda install -c conda-forge pyratbay

Docs at: https://github.com/pcubillos/pyratbay

Cite as:

.. code-block:: bibtex

